{"tid":504332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"球賽噓國歌　香港足總被只罰三千美元咋","createTime":"2017-12-19T23:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T11:23:38.000Z","uid":51271,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ff828cb94359cb3405ced05c527b6eb38e1c8955","tid":504332,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T23:59:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=247490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D247490&d=UkDqYGlYg9uUtnjJFx57ETOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f72e9f67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D247490&h=3b96521b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=247490</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】香港足球隊上月，對黎巴嫩的亞洲盃外圍賽再有觀眾噓國歌，亞洲足協對香港足總罰款三千美元。<br />\n<br />\n賽事上月十四日在大球場舉行，由香港足球隊主場迎戰黎巴嫩，賽前奏國歌部分觀眾發出噓聲，亞洲足協紀律和道德委員會上星期五開會討論，認為觀眾的行為違反條例，決定對香港足總罰款三千美元，並指若果再犯會有更嚴重處分。"},{"pid":"986412eba106099e5a47ba833d915aef956b558a","tid":504332,"uid":997,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T00:08:47.000Z","msg":"支那出左咁多黑錢收買人地都係罰得3000美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5220a2526d7c23ae7cc6a650a5bb4af49814a69a","tid":504332,"uid":5843,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"班唔睇波但係又係咁話閉門作賽嘅專家呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198e9fbd0e61de1b2b7e70085b5585556ff5066c","tid":504332,"uid":155080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T00:25:37.000Z","msg":"違反咗足協邊條條例？"},{"pid":"6d9ce5fb93653dedb9470a6dbe9a9d9b186e7bc5","tid":504332,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T00:38:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b79976fc7d1a063e9d11d65c8e89593a7346535","tid":504332,"uid":36780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r